// Projects Management Tools
// MCP tools for listing, registering, and unregistering projects in the project registry.

FUNCTION handleListProjects() -> { projects }                                    EXPORT
  CALLS: projectRegistry.list (project-registry)
  Retrieve all registered projects (invalid/stale entries are filtered by the registry).
  Return { projects }.

---

FUNCTION handleRegisterProject(args) -> { success, project?, error? }            EXPORT
  CALLS: projectRegistry.register (project-registry), projectRegistry.list (project-registry)
  Validate that the provided path is absolute. Return error if not.
  Register the project path via the registry.
  Look up the newly registered project in the list and return it.
  Return error response on any exception.

---

FUNCTION handleUnregisterProject(args) -> { success }                            EXPORT
  CALLS: projectRegistry.unregister (project-registry)
  Remove the project at the given path from the registry.
  Return { success } reflecting whether a project was actually removed.
